OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FToxic run-off from roads   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnot monitored, BBC finds   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,6,FA toxic mix of oil, chemicals and bits 
OL,7,Fof tyre from roads is polluting English
OL,8,Fwaterways and no-one is regularly      
OL,9,Fmonitoring it, the BBC has found.      
OL,11,FHeavy rain forces run-off into streams 
OL,12,Fand rivers. Campaigners say it causes  
OL,13,F'absolutely horrific' damage in places,
OL,14,Fincluding just downstream of where The 
OL,15,FGreat British Bake Off is filmed.      
OL,17,FEngland's major road network has more  
OL,18,Fthan 18,000 outflows or drains.        
OL,20,FNational Highways runs the network and 
OL,21,Fsays it's working to improve them.     
